    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ §1 OVERVIEW -->
    <div class="dp-section" id="overview">
      <div class="dp-section-header">
        <div class="dp-section-num">§1</div>
        <h2>System Overview</h2>
      </div>

      <p>The Validation Desk is the primary compliance and verification interface for central bank operators reviewing CBDC (Central Bank Issuance Bill) digital banknotes submitted by commercial banks. It is a Qt6 desktop application backed by a Rails 7.1 API.</p>
      <p>Every CBDC note entering the system must pass through the Validation Desk before it becomes live money. The desk enforces cryptographic authenticity, double-spend prevention, registry integrity, and compliance traceability.</p>

      <div class="dp-pane-grid">
        <div class="dp-pane dp-pane-left">
          <h3>Left Pane</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Batch summary bar</li>
            <li>Status filter rail</li>
            <li>Input mode selector</li>
            <li>Search bar (debounced)</li>
            <li>Import CBDC button</li>
            <li>Clear Table button</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dp-pane dp-pane-middle">
          <h3>Middle Pane</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Validation queue table (8 cols)</li>
            <li>Bulk Approve / Bulk Reject</li>
            <li>Persistent CBDC Preview</li>
            <li>Obverse + Reverse images</li>
            <li>Zoom controls</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dp-pane dp-pane-right">
          <h3>Right Pane + Properties</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Security Evidence panel</li>
            <li>Note details (read-only)</li>
            <li>Liquidity &amp; Trade context</li>
            <li>Decision controls</li>
            <li>Risk Intelligence panel</li>
            <li>Technical Manifest &amp; Compliance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Key Responsibilities</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Responsibility</th><th>Mechanism</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Signature validation</td><td>Ed25519 verify against registered IssuerKey via RbNaCl</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Double-spend detection</td><td>Serial lookup in CbdcNote registry; prior approval check</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Registry lookup</td><td><code>GET /api/v2/validation/registry_lookup/:serial</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Compliance verification</td><td>Gazette ref, backing type, seigniorage, authorization depth</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Risk scoring</td><td>risk_score 0–100: velocity + geofence + blacklist + missing fields</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Approval workflow</td><td><code>POST /api/v2/validation/approve</code> with operator signature</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Rejection workflow</td><td><code>POST /api/v2/validation/reject</code> with mandatory reason code</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Freeze (emergency)</td><td><code>POST /api/v2/validation/freeze</code> — locks asset system-wide</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ §2 DATA MODEL -->
    <div class="dp-section" id="data-model">
      <div class="dp-section-header">
        <div class="dp-section-num">§2</div>
        <h2>Data Models</h2>
      </div>

      <h3>ValidationSession — primary object per ingested note</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="f">session_ref</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Generated VAL-{hex} at ingest — shown in UI banner</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">serial</td><td class="t">string</td><td>From PNG serialNumber metadata</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">asset_code</td><td class="t">string</td><td>ISO 4217 e.g. NGN, KES, TZS</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">denomination</td><td class="t">integer</td><td>Face value — currency symbol stripped at ingest</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">issuer</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Full central bank name</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">issuer_key_id</td><td class="t">string</td><td>FK to issuer_keys.key_id</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">manifest_hash</td><td class="t">string</td><td>SHA-256 of batch manifest.json</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">payload_hash</td><td class="t">string</td><td>SHA-256 of individual note payload</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">issuer_sig</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Ed25519 signature, Base64URL encoded</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">signature_status</td><td class="t">enum</td><td><code>valid</code> | <code>invalid</code> | <code>unknown</code> | <code>pending</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">duplication_status</td><td class="t">enum</td><td><code>unique</code> | <code>duplicate</code> | <code>unchecked</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">final_decision</td><td class="t">enum</td><td><code>approved</code> | <code>rejected</code> | <code>flagged</code> | <code>frozen</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">decision_reason</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Required for reject and flag actions</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">decided_at</td><td class="t">datetime</td><td>UTC timestamp set on decision</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">risk_score</td><td class="t">integer</td><td>0–100 computed at ingest by risk engine</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">risk_flags</td><td class="t">jsonb[]</td><td>Array of triggered flags: velocity, geo, blacklist</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">approval_chain</td><td class="t">jsonb[]</td><td>[{operator_id, timestamp, action}] — multi-sig trail</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">required_approvals</td><td class="t">integer</td><td>Multi-sig threshold from governance config</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">liquidity_lock_id</td><td class="t">string</td><td>FK to LiquidityLock backing this note</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">batch_ref</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Links to CvibBatch from issuance system</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">batch_note_index</td><td class="t">integer</td><td>Position within batch e.g. 45</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">batch_note_total</td><td class="t">integer</td><td>Total notes in batch e.g. 1000</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">obverse_image_path</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Absolute path in storage/validation_images/</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>

      <h3>ValidationEvent — immutable audit log</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="f">session_ref</td><td class="t">string</td><td>FK to ValidationSession</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">serial</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Denormalized for fast audit queries</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">event_type</td><td class="t">enum</td><td><code>ingested</code> | <code>sig_verified</code> | <code>registry_checked</code> | <code>approved</code> | <code>rejected</code> | <code>flagged</code> | <code>frozen</code> | <code>exported</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">operator_id</td><td class="t">string</td><td>From Doorkeeper token</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">timestamp</td><td class="t">datetime</td><td>UTC — immutable once written, never updated</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">details</td><td class="t">jsonb</td><td>Event-specific payload e.g. { result: "invalid" }</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">node_id</td><td class="t">string</td><td>Node that recorded the event</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>

      <h3>Risk Score Factors</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Factor</th><th>Points</th><th>Trigger</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Velocity flag</td><td>+30</td><td>Serial appears in &gt;N transactions in rolling window</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Geofence flag</td><td>+25</td><td>Origin country outside authorized corridor region</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Blacklist flag</td><td>+45</td><td>Issuer, holder, or serial matches sanctions list</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Unverified signature</td><td>+15</td><td>signature_status ≠ valid at scoring time</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Missing backing lock</td><td>+10</td><td>liquidity_lock_id is null</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Score Range</th><th>Level</th><th>Action Required</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>0–39</td><td>Low</td><td>Standard review</td></tr>
          <tr><td>40–74</td><td>Elevated</td><td>Senior operator must approve</td></tr>
          <tr><td>75–100</td><td>HIGH RISK</td><td>Auto-flagged at ingest; explicit override confirmation required; excluded from bulk approve</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ §3 LEFT PANE -->
    <div class="dp-section" id="left-pane">
      <div class="dp-section-header">
        <div class="dp-section-num">§3</div>
        <h2>Left Pane — Validation Queue &amp; Filters</h2>
      </div>

      <h3>Batch Summary Bar</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Widget</th><th>Content</th><th>Update Trigger</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="f">lblValNodeStatus</td><td>● Online / ○ Offline</td><td>API reachability check</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">lblValBatchRef</td><td>Batch UUID or "—"</td><td>First imported note's batch_ref</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">lblValBatchTotal</td><td>{n} Notes pending</td><td>Every loadQueue() call</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">lblValBatchSelected</td><td>{n} Selected</td><td>Every checkbox itemChanged signal</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">lblValBatchProgress</td><td>{approved+rejected}/{total}</td><td>Every decision action</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">lblValRiskSummary</td><td>{n} Flagged or "No Flags"</td><td>Every loadQueue() call</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>

      <h3>Status Filter Rail</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Widget</th><th>SQL Filter</th><th>Default</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValFilterAll</td><td>No WHERE clause</td><td>✓ Selected on startup</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValFilterPending</td><td><code>final_decision IS NULL</code></td><td>—</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValFilterApproved</td><td><code>final_decision = 'approved'</code></td><td>—</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValFilterRejected</td><td><code>final_decision = 'rejected'</code></td><td>—</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValFilterFlagged</td><td><code>final_decision IN ('flagged','frozen')</code></td><td>—</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>

      <h3>Input Mode</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Widget</th><th>Behaviour</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValImportFile</td><td>btnValImportCBDC becomes visible; inbox auto-refresh timer stops</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValScanQR</td><td>Opens QR scanner dialog; result POSTs to <code>/api/v2/validation/parse_qr</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">rdoValInbox</td><td>Loads from <code>GET /api/v2/validation/inbox</code>; starts 30-second QTimer auto-refresh</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>

      <h3>Empty-Belt Startup</h3>
      <div class="dp-callout dp-warn"><span class="dp-ci">⚠</span><div><strong>The queue is always empty when the desk first opens.</strong> <code>m_tableCleared</code> defaults to <code>true</code>, so the automatic <code>loadQueue()</code> in <code>initialize()</code> is intentionally a no-op. The queue only populates after an explicit operator action: Import PNG, Scan QR, or switching to Inbox mode. This prevents stale sessions from a prior shift pre-populating the belt and guards against accidental double-approval of already-processed notes.</div></div>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Entry Point</th><th>Resets <code>m_tableCleared</code>?</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Application launch</td><td>No — starts <code>true</code></td><td>Belt is clear until the operator acts</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Import PNG (file dialog)</td><td>Yes → <code>false</code></td><td>Set in <code>onImportCBDC()</code> before <code>ingestFiles()</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Drag-and-drop PNG/ZIP</td><td>Yes → <code>false</code></td><td>Set in drop-zone <code>eventFilter</code> before <code>ingestFiles()</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Scan QR</td><td>Yes → <code>false</code></td><td>Set on successful QR parse</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Switch to Inbox mode</td><td>Yes → <code>false</code></td><td>Set in <code>onInputModeChanged()</code>; Inbox button also resets</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Clear Table button</td><td>Yes → <code>true</code></td><td>Belt clears; stays blank until next import</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Filter/search change</td><td>No</td><td><code>loadQueue()</code> returns early if already cleared</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>

      <h3>Import CBDC — btnValImportCBDC</h3>
      <div class="dp-rule">Accepted type: PNG only — validated by magic bytes 89 50 4E 47, not file extension.</div>
      <div class="dp-rule">File dialog: QFileDialog::getOpenFileNames — multiple files allowed in a single operation.</div>
      <div class="dp-rule">Endpoint: POST /api/v2/validation/ingest (multipart/form-data, file= param)</div>
      <div class="dp-rule">On success: m_tableCleared = false; m_sessionFilePaths[session_ref] = local_path; loadQueue()</div>
      <div class="dp-callout dp-warn"><span class="dp-ci">⚠</span><div>On 409 Conflict: show duplicate warning with existing session_ref — do not reload. On 422: show API error field, skip that file, continue with remaining files.</div></div>

      <h3>PNG Parsing — Validation::IngestService</h3>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>PNG Chunk</th><th>Keyword</th><th>Processing</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>tEXt</td><td>Comment</td><td>Parse directly as key=value\nstring</td></tr>
          <tr><td>zTXt</td><td>Comment</td><td>Skip keyword+null+compression_method byte, then Zlib::inflate</td></tr>
          <tr><td>iTXt</td><td>Comment (comp_flag=1)</td><td>Zlib::inflate the compressed text portion</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>
      <div class="dp-table-wrap"><table class="dp-table">
        <thead><tr><th>PNG Field</th><th>Rails Field</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="f">serialNumber</td><td class="f">serial</td><td>Verbatim</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">denomination</td><td class="f">denomination</td><td>gsub(/[^\d.]/, "").to_i — symbol stripped</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">asset_code / iso4217code</td><td class="f">asset_code</td><td>Uppercase ISO 4217</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">centralBank</td><td class="f">issuer</td><td>Full central bank name</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">issued_at</td><td class="f">issue_timestamp</td><td>ISO 8601 parsed to datetime</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">CBDCCreatedBy</td><td class="f">requested_by_operator</td><td>Minting operator handle</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">manifest_hash</td><td class="f">manifest_hash</td><td>SHA-256 hex</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">issuer_sig</td><td class="f">issuer_sig</td><td>Base64URL encoded Ed25519 signature</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="f">payload_hash</td><td class="f">payload_hash</td><td>SHA-256 hex of note payload</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table></div>
    </div>

